title: Canon Digital Camera Solution Disk v31.0 [Win+Mac]
description:
This torrent contains an iso image of the disk, which came included with Canon PowerShot 720 IS camera. It contains software, utilities and drivers for the camera.

The software includes Windows programs:
- ZoomBrowser EX 6.0
- PhotoStich 3.1
- Camera TWAIN Driver 6.8
- EOS Utility 1.1a

As well as Mac applications:
- ImageBrowser 6.0
- PhotoStich 3.2
- EOS Utility 1.1

Important! This CD needs to be mounted if you want to update your applications!
